text: Hey if you lot enjoyed this so much. Then I'd highly recommend giving Vermintide 2 a try on stream. It's similar to Left 4 Dead 2 in that its a team based survival trek through hostile missions with randomly generated waves of enemies. However where it stands out is a dedication to both melee and ranged combat, along with special abilities unique to the characters and a loadout system. Loot is another difference. Each character having a multitude of different weapons to choose from that drastically change their playstyle. Another big difference are the enemies. Instead of undead hordes. Vermintide 2 is populated mostly by the Skaven. Human sized rat men with a mob like mentality and devious souls. Their common troops are canon fodder to be fed into the meat grinder. However the smarter and more cunning among them utilize machines and devious tactics to take down the players. Machine guns, flamethrowers, poison bombs, tainted blades and titanic mutated variants of themselves. The threat doesn't stop there. Along with the Skaven are human allies. Chaos worshiping madmen that seek to see the world fall to the dark designs of their twisted Gods. They bring hellish flesh crafted abominations, hulking armoured soldiers, berserkers and life draining magic casters. Though that isn't even the last foe to face in this game. In the most recent update the Beastmen were unleashed. War loving minotaurs proficient in both magic and might. I hope just that little blurb has sold you on the game since I think you lot could have a fantastic time with the game.

They are quite good in this game since it is oike a decade old, but i can leave a few tips for future reference for them: If you see a witch, kill your lights and if you can avoid it then avoid it, if you cannot avoid it perform "Crowning" by using a shotgun and hitting the head. If none of you have shotguns use a chainsaw and saw it, no chainsaw? Go far from it and throw a molotov and shoot or just shoot it and run while still shooting.

If you see a hunter or jockey shoot fast, if it is in flight, time a good shove it can stumble it giving you time, a good tip is that the special infected are very weak against melee so always bring a melee weapon.

Smoker is hard to find but you can know one is there by weird coughing, i don't really know a way to dispatch it but sharp melee weapona can cut the tongue if someone is grabbed.

If you see a boomer shoot it, if you are near to it then shove it and fire, whatever you do, DO NOT USE A MELEE OR SHOOT IT CLOSE RANGE.

For a tank throw a molotov or use special ammo to kill it quickly.

If you see a charger well, move to the side quickly as shoving does nothing to stop it, to kill it fast use any melee weapon as it deals high damage to it, since bullets take more time.

For spitters well get out of the acid and just kill it, but avoid the place it died since there will be a patch of acid still there.

I do not know if you will see this but i hope it can help you if you do continue playing this.
